{"id": "1419619936032002048", "channel_id": "1419619936032002048", "type": 0, "author_id": "302718766289256448", "author_name": "zekiei", "author_bot": false, "content": "It feels like Aequor especially is suffering from the lack of Limiteds.\n\nHere's my point:\nGame launches, Tulu, Daff, Sorel and Lily release, one of each realm\nThen Murphy Wanda Salv 24, one of each again\nThen Thais Myriam Horla Ryker, good again \n\nBut after that: 4 Chaos 3 Caro 2 Ultra 1 Aequor, making a huge inbalance especially in late game.\nI really hope the coming awakers are Aequor->Ultra->Aequor->Caro->Ultra->Aequor or similar to balance the realms", "timestamp": "2025-09-22T09:42:48.013000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1419619936032002048", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」About Realm Inbalance, any plans to even out the number of limited units in each realms?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169144216686744", "1361169005435420785"]}
